                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5812" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0289</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8276 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“用爱成就伙伴”：西贝餐饮集团的文化探索之旅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Xibei Catering Group’s Journey of Cultural Exploration</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">屈燕妮，王文燕，刘彬鑫</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西贝餐饮集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党群部门/思想政治工作部门/企业文化部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西贝餐饮集团；企业文化；民营餐饮企业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Xibei Catering Group;The enterprise culture;Private Catering Enterprises</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了西贝餐饮集团高速成长并能在疫情期间共克时艰背后的文化基因。近年，在全国餐饮业面临极大挑战、许多餐饮企业举步维艰的情况下，西贝餐饮集团异军突起，从2012年60多家门店、13亿年营业收入，发展到2019年300多家门店、近60亿年营业收入，成为中餐炒菜领域龙头。2020年蔓延开的新冠肺炎疫情生死“大考”，西贝餐饮集团经受了考验并快速复苏。本案例描述西贝餐饮集团“用爱成就伙伴”的企业文化是如何形成的，又是如何落地的，西贝文化在驱动组织发展、帮助企业渡过难关中发挥的作用。以期对我国民营餐饮企业文化建设提供经验启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the cultural genes behind the rapid growth of Xibei Catering Group and its ability to overcome the difficulties during the epidemic period. In recent years, when the national catering industry is facing great challenges and many catering enterprises are struggling, Xibei Catering Group has risen to a new prominence. From more than 60 restaurants with an operating income of 1.3 billion yuan in 2012 to more than 300 restaurants with an operating income of nearly 6 billion yuan in 2019, Xibei has become the leader in the field of Chinese cooking. The COVID-19 epidemic in 2020 is a &quot;test of life and death&quot;. Xibei Restaurant Group has withstood the test and recovered quickly. This case describes how Xibei Catering Group&#39;s corporate culture of &quot;partnership with love&quot; was formed, and how it was implemented. It also describes the role of Xibei culture in driving the development of the organization and helping the enterprise to tide over the difficulties. It is expected to provide experience and inspiration for the cultural construction of private catering enterprises in China.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《企业文化》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业文化 制度管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-12</td>
